@startuml
actor NewUser
participant "Registration Page" as Register
participant "User Service" as UserService
participant "Payment Service" as PaymentService
participant "Stripe Payment Gateway" as Stripe

NewUser -> Register : Navigates to Registration Page
Register -> UserService : Enter Registration Information
UserService -> Register : Validate and Save Info
Register -> NewUser : Display Membership Options
NewUser -> Register : Selects PREMIUM Membership
Register -> Payment : Create Payment Session
Payment -> Stripe : Redirect to Payment
Stripe -> Payment : Complete Payment
Payment -> Register : Payment Success Notification
Register -> UserService : Create User Account
UserService -> Register : Return User Details
Register -> NewUser : Confirmation and Welcome
@enduml